{"lemma":"عَرِيضَةٍ","slug":"عَرِيضَةٍ","root":"ع.ر.ض","root_slug":"ع-ر-ض","root_link":"/words/roots/ع-ر-ض","pos":"ADJ","pos_camel":"adj","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"عَرِيض","root":"عرض","pos":"N","occurrence_count":1},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["adj"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":1},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n28706","n28711"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B9%D9%8E%D8%B1%D9%90%D9%8A%D8%B6%D9%8E%D8%A9%D9%8D"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"adj","gloss":"wide; broad"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"فَعِيل (faʕīl)-type stative-verb derived from the active participle from the verb عَرُضَ (ʕaruḍa, “to be or become wide”)."},"ipa":["/ʕa.riːdˤ/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n28706","headword_ar":"عَرِيضٌ","root":"ErD","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Broad,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"wide;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Mgh, O, Msb, K; *) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EuraADN","text_ar":"عُرَاضٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, O, K;) like as one says"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kabiyrN","text_ar":"كَبِيرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kubaArN","text_ar":"كُبَارٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S, O:) fem. of the former, (S, Msb,) and of the latter, (S, K,) with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"p","text_ar":"ة"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S, Msb, K:) the pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EariyDN","text_ar":"عَرِيضٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EiraADN","text_ar":"عِرَاضٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", like as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kiraAmN","text_ar":"كِرَامٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kariymN","text_ar":"كَرِيمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Msb.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EuraADapN","text_ar":"عُرَاضَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EuraADapN","text_ar":"عُرَاضَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A broad,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"wide, bow"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (S.) And ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EuraADaAtN","text_ar":"عُرَاضَاتٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^avarFA","text_ar":"اَثَرًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EuraADaAtN","text_ar":"عُرَاضَاتٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", in which the latter word is in the accus. case as a specificative, (S, O, TA,) meaning Camels"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"whose foot-marks are broad."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fulaAnN EariyDu AlbiTaAni","text_ar":"فُلَانٌ عَرِيضُ البِطَانِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Such a one is rich;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in a state of competence:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"possessed of much property."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, * O, K, * TA. [See also art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bTn","text_ar":"بطن"},{"kind":"text","text":".]) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EariyDu","text_ar":"عَرِيضُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlqafaA","text_ar":"القَفَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Fat:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) or (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"stupid."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EariyDu AlwisaAdi","text_ar":"عَرِيضُ الوِسَادِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Sleepy:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) or (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"stupid, dull,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"wanting in intelligence."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wsd","text_ar":"وسد"},{"kind":"text","text":".)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"duEaA='N EariyDN","text_ar":"دُعَا=ءٌ عَرِيضٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", occurring in the Kur [xli. 51], means (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Large,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"much, prayer,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"supplication:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, * TA:) or in this instance we may say"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"long."},{"kind":"text","text":"(L.)       -A2-  Also A goat (As, O, K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that is a year old,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"about a year old,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(As, O,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and that takes"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"crops"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the herbage"},{"kind":"text","text":"(As, O, K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and trees"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"shrubs"},{"kind":"text","text":"] (As, O)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with the side of his mouth:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) or (O, K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"such as is termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eatuwd","text_ar":"عَتُود"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q. v.], (S, O,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"when he rattles, and desires copulation:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, K:) or a ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"young"},{"kind":"text","text":"] goat"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"above such as is weaned and below such as is termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ja*aE","text_ar":"جَذَع"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q. v.]: or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"such as has pastured and become strong:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"such as is termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ja*aE","text_ar":"جَذَع"},{"kind":"text","text":": or a"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"young"},{"kind":"text","text":"goat"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"when he leaps the female:"},{"kind":"text","text":"it is applied only to"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a male:"},{"kind":"text","text":"the female is termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EariyDapN","text_ar":"عَرِيضَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": with the people of El-Hijáz it means peculiarly"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"such as is gelded:"},{"kind":"text","text":"it is also applied to a gazelle"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that has nearly become a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vaniY~","text_ar":"ثَنِىّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q. v.]: (TA:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EiroDaAnN","text_ar":"عِرْضَانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EuroDaAnN","text_ar":"عُرْضَانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S, O, K.)"}],"source_refs":["S","O","Msb","K","TA","A","As"]},{"entry_id":"n28711","headword_ar":"عِرِّيضٌ","root":"ErD","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Forward; officious; meddling; a busybody:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tyH","text_ar":"تيح"},{"kind":"text","text":":) one"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"who addresses himself to do evil to men."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, K.)"}],"source_refs":[]}]},"classical_definitions":null}